    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO GOLIATH ELECTRONICS!</h2><br><strong>CHAOS IN AISLE SEVEN</strong> is a retro action game where you play as George, a customer who shops for gifts in a store where salespeople are annoying, greedy and want to scam you for profit. Fight back by SHOUTING your displeasure in this over-the-top parody of shopping!<br>Filled with humour and parodying over-the-top mundane shopping situations, help George take down the Goliath corporation by shouting as loud as possible to anyone in your way. You will shop for electronics, groceries, furniture, a car and much more!",
